snippet.title: Julie Dawn Olsen
snippet.description:
Hey, I'm Julie I love sharing about makeup, fashion, fitness, faith and whatever I am currently into!  
My goal is to inspire and show you that affordable makeup can look like high-end!  I love finding a diamond in the rough and I want to share that feeling with you. So, If you're like me and love finding out which drugstore products are high-quality and which high-end products are actually worth the splurge then subscribe to my channel!  Become part of my YouTube family, I would love to get to know you, become friends and I'll teach you everything I know and love about makeup!
xo Julie
